## Diffusion Overview

Diffusion Models are state-of-the-art Generative AI models that have been getting a lot of attention
lately. They have been surprisingly powerful in many different domains. Whether its creating photo-realistic
pictures of imaginary people, sample of songs from a prompt, or even never seen before levels of weather
predictions. 

---

## Simple Diffusion

$ Diffusion Diagram

Diffusion works by taking data, adding noise, and trainging a neural net to remove noise from the data.
Once the model has a strong idea of how to denoise data in a particular domain, generation is done by giving
the model isotropic gaussian noise. This contains no meaningful signal of any piece of data in particular,
so it generates something new.

